column34: After all the testimonies presented from Amber heard, her pictures circulated with no time or day strip, obviously manipulated too which I can smash my face if I want on photoshop must be withdrawn from evidence. She looks perfect in all public appearances after the claimed abuses and happy. She is a disgrace to all us women who have suffered domestic abuse and many like myself even in a foreign country with nowhere to go, but I made it. I didn't beg him after the events which she did.
